Package: cauda
Title: Causal Automated Unified Data Analysis
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Aadi", "Soni", , "mr.aadi.soni@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A simple, high-level toolkit for exploratory causal data
    analysis. Provides automated causal discovery, graph editing,
    correlation networks, partial dependence plots, decision optimization,
    and conditional independence testing for tabular data frames.
